How EAG Paris sandboxes can help to feel more confortable with Redhat Openshift and IBM Cloud Pak technologies.

<p dir="ltr">In Q4 2019 EAG Paris started delivering on premise plateform to help business partner getting familiar with IBM Cloud Pak.</p>

<p dir="ltr">For several month now, EAG Paris sandboxes offer the possibility to dry run Openshift, Cloud Paks and cartridges installation before experimenting those complexe technologies on customer site.</p>

<p dir="ltr">French and also Business Partner from Spain and Benelux are already experiencing.</p>

<p dir="ltr">This <a href="https://github.com/bpshparis/sandbox/blob/master/Installing-Redhat-Openshift-3.11-on-VMware-vSphere-Hypervisor.md" target="_blank">article</a> is the first of a series that will cover on premise IBM Cloud Pak on Redhat Openshift experience...</p>

